message.body: What time are you getting in on Saturday??
Can't wait to see you tomorrow!!
:) :) :) me too. Reservations at a French bistro tomorrow before theatre fest 2012
Ok, sounds great! Will do, I can't wait to see you and have you meet Fernando!!
Yayyyyy :)!!! Me too. Safe travels!
Just made in on time!!! Will Carolyn be there??
On the bus? Great! No, her ride fell through. But if Brett can come he has that comp so that's good news :)
Oh bummer, I wanted to see that biatch. Yeah, like last ones on, sat down, and bus left!!
Wooooo close one exciteddddddd
I see Philly, haven't crossed the bridge yet
Landed yet?
Awesome!
Just got off, at 8th and market, take the pathco right?
Ok, just at the rite aid
Lmk!
He's on his way - he's already in the neighborhood. His phone number is in the previous text! So just let him know where you're at :)
Everything good?
Is fern coming? Too sick?
Yep, on my way!!
He is too sick :/
Yeah, he is sleeping and I got him food for when he gets hungry
What station do I transfer
Hey baby, I'm sooooo sorry I'm missing it right now!!! I'm at the place but it's locked :/
Oh em geee, crazy story to tell. I'm back at your place... :/
Are you staying in tonight or would you want to go out? I can come home to hang out too
I think just staying in, im exhausted...
But we r boring, don't feel like u need to come back home - go out, celebrate!!
Well we told some people that we'd get a drink so I'm going out for a bit and then coming home if you're still up!
Ok, hope it went well, so freakin dumb that I didn't make it!
Hey baby, whenever u wake up can u let me know where to grab a towel? Fern and I can use the same one...
Didn't tell me you love right next to the rock school!!
Oh hah, yea!
On the bus, thanks so much for letting us stay at your place! Besos
Oh good - I hope you had a good afternoon! What did you do?

Actualllly we walked to the museum but then hopped on a tour bus since fern felt shitty. It was nice and easy. The bus got stuck in that really wealthy part and some Philly bystander guys had to LIFT the car and move it!!
Oh my god! Oh is he feeling better yet?
A little bit, Claire is feeling shitty too so it was a strong vaccine
Oh and we saw John Collins at the station!
